{"tid":463732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ON9無極限]池袋水族館一晚死左1235條魚","createTime":"2017-11-09T19:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T02:16:20.000Z","uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"43318a61c7a3d3440988303ec1bb446b155e9609","tid":463732,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:34:57.000Z","msg":"位於日本東京池袋的Sunshine水族館（サンシャイン水族館），昨日（11月8日）館內大魚池有24品種共1235條魚死亡，疑因池內供氧不足導致。 大魚池今日（11月9日）重開時只剩73條魚倖存，生還率僅6%，原定的潛水餵魚表演項目亦要暫停。 涉事魚池有12米長、9.6米闊、2.4米高，為Sunshine水族館內最大魚池。初步調查指，水族館日前在池水加入藥物為部份魚類治療，為讓藥效更好把換氣系統關閉，但職員事後忘記重開系統，池內氧氣持續下降，導致魚類缺氧大量死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-09-2017/42458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-09-2017%2F42458&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNvzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=95dfd4f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-09-2017/42458</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 有對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipen_3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipen_3&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNvzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=741fc23b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ipen_3</a>"},{"pid":"9eb51f46ad77faa55f205dfcb374aba3a83bae92","tid":463732,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22607ac1128db41428f1b8bdc28ae9f911ea6c7f","tid":463732,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:45:16.000Z","msg":"炒得"},{"pid":"7d944651a821c0b89da666ece8ec511f199b6c0b","tid":463732,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:54:44.000Z","msg":"熱血時報.."},{"pid":"7a0dbba2952c25df6abe5d419f9d283c86eb1f3a","tid":463732,"uid":84360,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:02:03.000Z","msg":"果6%:想當年我無氧氣都捱到 呢家啲後生真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 